title: Darkness on the Edge of Town Paranormal Radio Show 2006 complete
description:
This is my first try at creating a torrent.

I'm not always on the computer and I do not let it run when I leave for work.

Typically I can let this torrent run from about 9pm to 5am M-F Eastern Time.


This torrent is of the very first year of the paranormal radio show Darkness on the Edge of Town hosted by Dave Schrader out of Minneapolis.

Enjoy .... if it works. :-)
